  "action_input": "{ \"prompt\": \"A professional 3D isometric pyramid architecture diagram with four distinct, separated horizontal layers. Bottom layer (OBJECT LAYER): Yellow (#FFC000), featuring icons of UI components and libraries. Second layer (ENGINE LAYER): Green (#70AD47), featuring a row of 7 engine/gear icons. Third layer (SKILL LAYER): Orange (#ED7D31), featuring symbols of orchestration and workflow nodes. Top layer (COGNITIVE LAYER): Blue (#5B9BD5), featuring an AI brain and rule engine icon. Style: Clean infographic, professional business presentation look, white background, subtle drop shadows for depth, thin arrows indicating upward data flow between layers. High resolution, clear labels for each layer.\", \"size\": \"1024x1024\" }",
